metadata.name: Portugal coast
metadata.description:
As the sun sets over the rugged cliffs of the Portuguese coast, the sky transforms into a canvas of orange, pink, and purple hues. The gentle breeze carries the salty scent of the Atlantic as the waves crash against the rocky shore.

Seagulls soar overhead, their cries blending with the distant sound of fishing boats returning to port. A lone fisherman casts his line into the water, hopeful for a catch that will sustain his livelihood.

Further down the coast, hidden coves and secret beaches beckon to be explored. The crystal-clear waters invite swimmers and surfers alike to dive in and ride the waves.

The vibrant colors of the traditional fishing villages stand out against the backdrop of the stunning natural scenery. Cobblestone streets wind through narrow alleys, leading to quaint cafes and shops offering fresh seafood and locally made crafts.

As the night falls, the sound of Fado music drifts through the air, adding to the enchanting atmosphere of this coastal paradise. Portugal'
